{"tid":1045162,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"9000人擠爆林口體育館 BLACKPINK：不要推擠會受傷","createTime":"2019-03-03T12:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T10:15:35.000Z","uid":74065,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"adbf5fced64aca1e54bf5a5647b884798451c9cc","tid":1045162,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣女團BLACKPINK於2019年展開世界巡演，3日終於來到台灣站，這也是她們出道以來首次造訪寶島，4位女孩穿著粉白色搭配的套裝亮麗登場，以《DDU-DU DDU-DU》、《Forever Young》開場，演出雖延遲26分開始，依舊將氣氛炒得嗨翻天。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3932/d3932547.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3932%2Fd3932547.jpg&h=7216c0f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK於3日在台灣開唱。（圖／資料照／翻攝自YG）<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK 3日在林口體育館舉辦個人專場演唱會，可惜天公不作美，下起大雨，演出延遲26分才開始，但並未因此澆熄粉絲的熱情，4人坐著升降台霸氣亮相，全場9000人響起熱烈尖叫，她們以中文自我介紹，用可愛地音調喊著「我是智秀」、「我是彩英」、「我是Lisa」、「我是Jeinne」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3932/d3932548.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3932%2Fd3932548.jpg&h=ab36d259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK演唱會吸引9000人朝勝。（圖／翻攝自YG）<br />\n<br />\nJisoo成為中文擔當代表，她用中文率先問好「我們很想你們」，Lisa則是甜喊「大家興奮嗎？」台下大喊「興奮」，她反而害羞小聲回應「me too」，可愛度爆棚，搖滾區塞滿觀眾，Rose也用英文呼籲「不要推擠喔，這樣會受傷。」心繫歌迷安全。<br />\n<br />\nPPT班死台狗成日笑人要送飛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed37a3b654757cfa9b23db2e35783fc0e1ae5389","tid":1045162,"uid":73404,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:16:42.000Z","msg":"8500送飛<br />\n500推擠<br />\n<br />\n尖叫+500 <br />\n失禁+1000<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8eaaf191e7c92b31ed44be9fccb06088e2d0b6","tid":1045162,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:23:00.000Z","msg":"我推車jennie"},{"pid":"898b39f1557d2da3756a70244bf8cec5c31e0f47","tid":1045162,"uid":171594,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:23:39.000Z","msg":"試吓抽起solo<br />\n淨係得其餘三個<br />\n睇吓銷情係點"},{"pid":"f17b2fd859e4d3c752baa7a19f4cdf4eed20b29e","tid":1045162,"uid":74065,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:24:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 六點半開始7:50結束</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846ddeca915f3180601573f788f76be0ba5ed017","tid":1045162,"uid":165368,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f17b2fd859e4d3c752baa7a19f4cdf4eed20b29e","tid":1045162,"uid":74065,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:24:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 六點半開始7:50結束</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:47:15.000Z","msg":"落雨天留客天留bp不留"},{"pid":"4a5b88a760170fd4c59856406c90e79c17a86581","tid":1045162,"uid":14670,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f17b2fd859e4d3c752baa7a19f4cdf4eed20b29e","tid":1045162,"uid":74065,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T12:24:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 六點半開始7:50結束</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/b